sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer)
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Controller as Controller Manager
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Storage as External Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure/PVC)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>MM: gRPC Inference Request<br/>Port 8033 | Optional TLS/mTLS
        MM->>etcd: Check model placement<br/>gRPC/2379 | Optional TLS/mTLS
        etcd-->>MM: Model location & routing info
        MM->>Runtime: Forward to loaded model<br/>gRPC localhost/UDS
        Runtime-->>MM: Inference result
        MM-->>Client: gRPC Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: REST Inference via OAuth
        Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS REST Request<br/>Port 8443 | TLS | OAuth Token
        OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate OpenShift OAuth token<br/>SAR: get services in namespace
        OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: HTTP Forward<br/>Port 8008 | localhost (pre-auth)
        RESTProxy->>MM: Translate HTTP→gRPC<br/>Port 8033 | Optional TLS (localhost)
        MM->>Runtime: Forward to model<br/>gRPC localhost/UDS
        Runtime-->>MM: Inference result
        MM-->>RESTProxy: gRPC Response
        RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP Response
        OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Controller,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Read Predictor/InferenceService CR<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
        Controller->>MM: registerModel / setVModel<br/>gRPC/8033 | Optional TLS/mTLS
        MM->>etcd: Store model registration<br/>gRPC/2379 | Credentials
        MM->>Puller: Request model load
        Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 | Storage credentials
        Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
        Puller->>Runtime: Load model<br/>gRPC/8085 or UDS
        Runtime-->>Puller: Model loaded
        Puller-->>MM: Load complete
        MM->>etcd: Update model state
        etcd-->>Controller: Model state change event<br/>(via EventStream watcher)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor status<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Controller Reconciliation
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event<br/>(ServingRuntime/Predictor change)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Read etcd Secret<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
        Controller->>Controller: Render deployment template<br/>(14-step transformation pipeline)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Headless Service<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update HPA (if autoscaling)<br/>HTTPS/443 | SA Token
    end
